<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-center has-outfit-fo=
nt-family" id=3D"whatisreadtime" style=3D"margin-bottom:60px;font-size:42px=
">More on Reading Time Estimation</h2>



<div class=3D"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-top has-lor=
a-font-family is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-ec2e7a44 w=
p-block-columns-is-layout-flex" style=3D"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0">
<div class=3D"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-outfit-font-fam=
ily is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<h4 class=3D"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-outfit-font-family ha=
s-medium-font-size">What is Reading Time?</h4>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Reading time is the time taken for an aver=
age person to silently read a piece of text while maintaining reading compr=
ehension. Based on the meta-analysis of 100's of studies involving over 180=
00 participants, the average silent reading speed for an adult individual h=
as been estimated to be approximately 238 words per minute <a href=3D"https=
://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0749596X19300786" target=
=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener"><span style=3D"text-decoration: und=
erline;">(Marc Brysbaert, 2019)</span></a></p>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">The average reading time for a piece of te=
xt can thus be deduced by dividing the total word count by 238.</p>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Mathematical formula for calculating readi=
ng time in minutes:</p>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Reading Time =3D Total Word Count / 238</p=
>



<h4 class=3D"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-outfit-font-family ha=
s-medium-font-size">What is Speech Time?</h4>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Speech time is the time taken for an avera=
ge person to read aloud a piece of text. Based on the meta-analysis of near=
ly 80 studies involving 6000 participants, the average oral reading speed f=
or an adult individual is considered to be 183 words per minute <a href=3D"=
https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0749596X19300786" da=
ta-type=3D"link" data-id=3D"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/a=
bs/pii/S0749596X19300786" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener"><sp=
an style=3D"text-decoration: underline;">(Marc Brysbaert, 2019)</span></a>.=
</p>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">The average speech time of a piece of text=
 can thus be deduced by dividing the total word count by 183. </p>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Marc Brysbaert's paper further states that=
 reading speeds are generally lower for older adults, children and readers =
with english as a second language.</p>
</div>



<div class=3D"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-outfit-font-fam=
ily is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<h4 class=3D"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-outfit-font-family ha=
s-medium-font-size">How To Use Our Read Time Estimation Tool?</h4>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Input text by copying &amp; pasting or upl=
oading PDF, DOCX or TXT files, or just directly enter the word count in num=
ber format.</p>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">The tool instantly calculates both read al=
oud and silent reading times based on the word count and average reading sp=
eeds of 183 WPM and 238 WPM.</p>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Adjust the speed sliders to match your per=
sonal reading speed to see updated reading times in real time. If you aren'=
t sure of your reading speed, get it tested with our <a href=3D"https://the=
readtime.com/reading-speed-test/"><span style=3D"text-decoration: underline=
;">free reading speed test</span></a>.</p>



<h4 class=3D"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-outfit-font-family ha=
s-medium-font-size">How Long Does It Take To Read 1000 Words?</h4>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Assuming the average reading speed of an a=
dult is 238 words per minute, it takes approximately 4 minutes and 12 secon=
ds to read 1000 words.</p>



<h4 class=3D"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-outfit-font-family ha=
s-medium-font-size">How Long Does It Take To Read 100 Pages?</h4>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Assuming a page consists of 500 words, it =
approximately takes 3 hours and 30 minutes to read 100 pages.</p>



<h4 class=3D"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-outfit-font-family ha=
s-medium-font-size">How Long Does It Take To Speak 1000 Words?</h4>



<p class=3D"has-text-align-left">Given that the average oral reading speed =
of an adult individual is 183 words per minute, it takes approximately 5 mi=
nutes and 28 seconds to orate 1000 words.</p>
</div>
</div>



